a little bit of red pepper, and I'm gonna

00:00:36.520 --> 00:00:46.010
put that in there also, and I'm just gonna
whisk this together to make this delicious

00:00:46.010 --> 00:00:47.010
and simple marinade.

00:00:47.010 --> 00:00:51.940
You know, most of this stuff you probably
have in your cupboard already, in your spice

00:00:51.940 --> 00:00:53.470
cabinet.

00:00:53.470 --> 00:00:54.980
Super-duper easy!

00:00:54.980 --> 00:01:00.580
