shake and shimmy it around to make sure that

00:01:17.240 --> 00:01:20.040
every wing gets really well coated.

00:01:20.040 --> 00:01:28.460
And then, what you wanna do once you got them
really well coated is you wanna just put them

00:01:28.460 --> 00:01:31.170
in the refrigerator for a few hours.

00:01:31.170 --> 00:01:35.140
If you can, ideally put them in overnight
`cause the longer they soak in, the more they're

00:01:35.140 --> 00:01:36.600
gonna suck up that flavor.

00:01:36.600 --> 00:01:40.400
Then, once they've been in the refrigerator
for a few hours, you're just gonna take `em

00:01:40.400 --> 00:01:43.659
