Before you do that, you wanna pre-heat your
oven to 450 degrees, and what you're gonna

00:01:49.380 --> 00:01:56.070
do is you're gonna put your wings in there
for 10 minutes, and you're gonna cook `em

00:01:56.070 --> 00:01:57.070
uncovered.

00:01:57.070 --> 00:02:01.820
So, when you're done with your 10 minutes
in the oven at 450 degrees, you're gonna take

00:02:01.820 --> 00:02:03.380
whatever is left of your marinade.

00:02:03.380 --> 00:02:07.560
You're gonna brush it on the wings and put
them back in for another 15 to 20 minutes,

00:02:07.560 --> 00:02:10.750
